        public static Type getTypeFromClass(java.lang.Class<?> typeClass,
                                    Schema schema,
                                    SchemaFactory factory,
                                    java.util.Map<java.lang.String,Type> cache)
                             throws UnknownTypeException
        Creates a type the type can be primitive, based on the Primitives definitions the type can be klass, if it is already defined and added in the cache
        Parameters:
        typeClass - the class of the type
        schema - the schema which the type belongs to
        factory - a schema factory to create new types with
        cache - a type cache that keeps the definitions of klass types
        Returns:
        a new type
        Throws:
        UnknownTypeException - if no type found
